name: Fresh Lifestyle Tee Black on White
description: Fresh is a sub group of the Collateral, created by Arnie Giancana for inner city young people; it’s focus is on abolishing segregation through music by UK artistes working together on collaborations and music based projects. Fresh Tees can be seen in the Keep Fresh music video now showing on youtube & arniegiancana.com
